## ia-docs configuration
## Place this file at the root of your project.

## The directory subtree to enforce documentation for.
## The hook will only inject docs when editing files under this path.
## Examples: "src", "backend/src", "packages/api/src", "app"
SOURCE_DIR=src

## The filename to use for documentation files.
## Default: IA-docs.md — you can change this to anything.
DOC_FILENAME=IA-docs.md
